description: Lovely historic detail is the hallmark of this condominium in Van Vorst Park. This is a sought-after parlor floor level one-bedroom condo. The home is ideally located just 2.5 blocks from the Grove Street PATH station. Original details include floor-to-ceiling windows, crown moldings, wood floors, high ceilings, two marble mantels and some exposed brick. There are a washer and dryer in unit. Very low monthly maintenance fee and taxes.
